Class AbstractAsset

  • java.lang.Object
    • bisq.asset.AbstractAsset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Asset
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Coin, Token

    public abstract class AbstractAsset
extends java.lang.Object
implements Asset
    Abstract base class for Asset implementations. Most implementations should not extend this class directly, but should rather extend Coin, Token or one of their subtypes.
    Since:
    0.7.0
